:'''Virtual Seymour:''' Hi, player (Trailblazer). Did you miss me? Come play the thrilling Hexanexus: Remake if you did!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Aren't you eating prison goop?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Prisoners can also grant their image rights?
:'''Virtual Seymour:''' Heh, I developed this entire Empathic Immersia system. It'd be absurd if they didn't even allow me to show my face, would it?
:'''Virtual Seymour:''' This virtual NPC system was made possible with Arma Correctional Group's writing and my development. You stand before the great creator of this Empathic Immersia!
:'''Virtual Seymour:''' What do you think? Any thoughts?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You got something I haven't played before?
