::'''Virtual Seymour:''' That fellow looks a little... imposingly dignified. We fear he might scare off temple fair guests, so he's really not suitable to be a guide.
::Can I skip the gameplay? I just want the reward.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why hasn't Arma shown himself then?
