:'''Virtual Seymour:''' You're also a Hexanexus veteran. There's nothing much that I can guide as a... guide.
:'''Virtual Seymour:''' I'm off, have fun. Hope you liked the design of this puzzle.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You'd probably better tell me about the rules again.
::'''Virtual Seymour:''' Nope, we're almost at the 800-word limit. Goodbye!
